t ut\u00f8vende musiker i dag, sier Ekle.", "Etter \u00e5 ha erfart effekten av alexanderteknikken bestemte han seg for \u00e5 g\u00e5 samme vei. Han er n\u00e5 nyutdannet alexanderl\u00e6rer - klar til \u00e5 ta imot nye elever i \u00e5ret da hundre\u00e5rsjubileet for Alexanders teknikk blir markert over store deler av verden."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "da557ff50dd25d89504a9e18e92d48bf13cd6fe79f3b23b05c1092f411ea3c57"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-09-01T14:26:37.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- Hvisk a-a-a-a... Tenk p\u00e5 noe ekstra hyggelig - og pr\u00f8v igjen. Flott! N\u00e5 har stemmen klar bane..."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1121975.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20Alexanderl55"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ed54b19fe06109e422ec2cc6a6580413b5671a71.jpg?59886716"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "F\u00e5r kroppen i vater -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "ed54b19fe06109e422ec2cc6a6580413b5671a71"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["hode", "smerter", "hvisk a-a-a-a", "kroppen", "musiker", "elever"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["u. men", "institutt", "purpur", "alexanders", "petter", "the constructive teaching centre"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["london", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["\u00f8yvind brandtz\u00e6gs", "rita abrahamsen", "sigur